io.springlets.data.web.datatables

Class DatatablesData<T>

  • java.lang.Object
    • io.springlets.data.web.datatables.DatatablesData<T>
  • Type Parameters:
    T - Response data type
    Direct Known Subclasses:
    ConvertedDatatablesData

    public class DatatablesData<T>
extends Object
    Response data for data requests performed by datatables component. This class will be converted to JSON, so the property names must follow the name of the properties expected by datatables.
    Author:
    Cèsar Ordiñana at http://www.disid.com[DISID Corporation S.L.]

    • Constructor Detail

      • DatatablesData

        public DatatablesData(List<T> data,
                      Long recordsTotal,
                      Long recordsFiltered,
                      Integer draw)
        Create a response for datatables with data obtained from a previous request.
        Parameters:
        data - the data to show
        recordsTotal - the total number of available data
        recordsFiltered - the number of data after filtering
        draw - counts datatables requests. It must be sent by datatables value in the data request.

      • DatatablesData

        public DatatablesData(Integer draw,
                      String error)
        Create an error response to datatables.
        Parameters:
        draw - counts datatables requests. It must be sent by datatables value in the data request.
        error - the error produced to inform the user

      • DatatablesData

        Create an answer for datatables with data obtained from a previous request.
        Parameters:
        data - the data to show
        recordsTotal - the total number of available data
        recordsFiltered - the number of data after filtering
        draw - counts datatables requests. It must be sent by datatables value in the data request.
        error - (optional) the produced error to inform the user

      • DatatablesData

        public DatatablesData(org.springframework.data.domain.Page<T> dataPage,
                      Long recordsTotal,
                      Integer draw)
        Create an answer for datatables with data obtained from a previous request.
        Parameters:
        dataPage - the page of the obtained data
        recordsTotal - the total number of data with no filter and no pagination
        draw - counts datatables requests. It must be sent by datatables value in the data request.
